snippet.title: HOW DiD SHE DO THAT¿?¿  ultimate Family dance party, painting rocks, Adley & Niko play a new game!
snippet.description:
The kids learning how to hang upside down 😂
and YOUR MERCH IS BACK!!   http://aforadley.com/

JOIN OUR FAM!! --- http://goo.gl/rfgp8V

Best Daredevil Day Ever 1155

One of the families favorite things about October is all of the Halloween decorations. Jenny, Adley and Niko Bear found some awesome bats that go perfect for the holiday and decide to hang them on the door. Adley, being the loving little girl that she is, groups them in families and names them after all of us. 

Once the door is all decorated, the find me downstairs so they can show me the great job that they did. After decorations, Adley comes up with a brand new game called statue! the rules are easy, Adley and Niko are statues, Jenny sells them, and I buy them. But they are crazy. The Adley statue moves around when I'm not looking while the Niko Bear statue has a button to make it come a live and run around the room. haha I love pretend play with the kiddos!!

With the new game done, I have to show you guys a new trick that the kiddos and I learned. We can hang from the ceiling in the kitchen!! It's hilarious, though Jenny wishes we didn't use the house like a park toy. We then head to the backyard splash pad to find some rocks for arts and crafts time.

We love doing little DIY creative projects with the kiddos, but these are extra special, because we are going to take these rocks to the construction site of a brand new LDS Temple. These temples are super important to us, so its awesome that we get to put little memories into the foundation. Adley draws pretty flowers, Niko colors his rock so good, and Jenny makes a cute rock for her and baby Navey and I make a rock about our family and how much we love each other. ( Also with a little pirate theme for pirate island lol)

After dropping of the rocks and doing some work at the lake lot, I'm home for the night! I also brought gifts for the whole family. We have A for Adley shirts again!! We have a brand new company making them and they look so good. The colors are bright, the images look great, and we are excited to share them with you guys again!! Prices are still the same, we want them to be easy for you to get. If you bought a shirt before and there were problems with it, we want to help. After unboxing the surprise, it's time to start our bed time routine and end this amazing Best Day Ever!!

snippet.title: Chuggington StackTrack unboxing kids toy Chungginton train Super Slow motion trains Disney review
snippet.description:
Unboxing Chuggington StackTrack a stackable toy for kids with the Chuggington train. This toy set of Chungington features Koko, the green train. With super slow motion video footage.
In this unboxing video for kids we will find the Chuggington StackTrack a Working WheelsService Yard Set with Koko Lola, which is the official name for this Chuggington toy set. Jus like Thomas and Friends this is a great toy for kids.

This Chunggington train toy set is very similar to the Thomas and friends trains, it includes tracks and a ramp, where Koko can perform jumps! Have you ever seen trains jump? This stackable train track lets kids learn and build their own train tracks. It can be customized in unlimited ways and this box includes the green train called Koko.

Koko Lola train is an electric engine train. She is a little bit green and purple and she was built for really high speeds. That makes her one of the fastest Chuggers in Chuggington she love adventures and in this toys set she will even jump!
Kids know Chunggington from the disney cartoons aired on Nickelodeon and Nick Jr and Disney Junior tv channels. This Chuggington StackTrack we're unboxing in this video for kids is appropriate for children of 3 years and up. Launch Koko and jump! This kids train set of chungington is great fun to play with. Connect this set to other Stack 

Track sets of Chunggington. For example if you already have Brewster and Wilson which are the other advanced trainees. The chuggers and trainees of chinggington are waiting for you to build some train tracks. Watch this fun kids video on youtube and see what the chungington train stack track looks like. If you've seen the Disney junior chuggington cartoons, then you'll probably like this unboxing video too.

Be sure to like our video and subscribe to see more!

snippet.title: Voice Controlled RC Car with SmartWatch TomTop KFToys Unboxing Review
snippet.description:
Available for $13.99 at TOMTOP
http://www.tomtop.com/car-toys-1175/p-rm5989.html?aid=817X

If you love remote controlled toys, you will love the mini remote controlled smart watch voice command car. Car comes with flashing lights from inside the car when you turn on the button under the car, then means the car is stand-by commands from smart watch. The car also has 2.4Ghz relative frequency connection, after first connection, the car will default the smart watch which you already connected. 

Features:
High sturdy car body.
Powerful high speed motor.
Three different speed mode.
Smart watch voice command.
LED head lights actually light up.
2.4Ghz relative frequency connection.
1/30 scale suitable for indoor and outdoor control.
RC control goes backward and forward, steers left and right.
Built-in rechargeable battery, computer USB power supply directly.
